\id TIT - Sembeleke Samberigi PNG Titus 01 22/3/91 Macnaughtan 
\h TAITASI 
\toc1 Polomaęž‰ Taitasi paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyeke wapee 
\toc2 Taitasi 
\toc3 Taitasi 
\mt1 Polomaęž‰ Taitasi paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyeke wapee  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 IĚ±taęž‰ Polomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali hataęž‰ make Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ aposolo hali hataęž‰ make do wape wapitolome. IĚ±taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ maĚ±leke lilaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hone tulalemeeki daeyaenaęž‰ lono ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± mea tapaeyaęž‰me. Kuta make ikaęž‰ pi miniki haasaęž‰ haunaęž‰ otaęž‰ pitaęž‰ miniki haenaęž‰ walonoyeke IĚ± tapaeyaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Ikaęž‰ mo koto hone tulalemeeki make mo otaęž‰ pi miniki halemeeki make do hau yaapotaęž‰ mo deto halaęž‰ haunaęž‰ ti laasaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ ti lalememe. Mo yayapiki pi na lo halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ mo alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao na wepia winaęž‰ leke do deto halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ pi laęž‰ wiekeme.  
\v 3 Koto hoki nanetaęž‰ mo yapekeyeke nate opolo epeke pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo koto deto halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi walaasaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ walemeke pimaęž‰ peneme yaeyekeme. Koto kaęž‰laęž‰ pitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ walawano mo nikaęž‰ daęž‰taasaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ peae laęž‰leke walaasome.   
\p
\v 4 Koto ekinaęž‰ do wapetaęž‰ mo Taitasi paęž‰taęž‰ wape tapaasome. Mo dikaęž‰ hone tulaalope ekinaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ ya weki halaęž‰me. Mo Apaęž‰ halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ make mo nikaęž‰ daęž‰taasaęž‰ Ketiso Yesumaęž‰ make neke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ puki lopao haasaęž‰eki yaapo kinaęž‰e la alome.   
\s1 Siosi you haliwekinaęž‰ manaęž‰ pi  
\p
\v 5 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ niki na pumaęž‰ ekimanu tikitiki yao epeaotaęž‰ mo siosi tapake handeteke halo peleme haliweki make mo daoni paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ lolenaęž‰yeke neke hae laa pomaęž‰me. Neke mo Kotiti ikali hoki tukikinaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao poaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ do ekinaęž‰ puaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ hande dupa piaęž‰peke loaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone wiaęž‰peke.  
\v 6 Mo handeteke halo paęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ moeki aęž‰ndaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰ hali make wandaęž‰ homeke maęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰ hapeke yelieke. Kutupa make ipikaęž‰ wekiwandikitaęž‰ mo pi miniki hataęž‰ ikitaęž‰ ti teke yokaęž‰laęž‰ wekiwandikie o ateke inkikinaęž‰ pi yokaęž‰laęž‰ wekiwandikie laa ikaęž‰ biki na wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hapaęž‰peke yelimikie.  
\v 7 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hau handeteke hapeke ekinaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ na piki hali hapeke yelieke. Ipikitaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali lu pambaake pi lo o mineke aĚ±iĚ± koto kone pankaęž‰laęž‰ o hoke ikali naa keao o wandaęž‰hali make alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ hoeyao tekipuleke lao o IĚ± IĚ± laa pasaęž‰tei pu o dupiki haumanu pu haliaęž‰ halitaęž‰ hapeke na yelieke.  
\v 8 Ipikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ kimisu wandaęž‰hali pambolo opolo pinaęž‰ alaęž‰ hali make epeke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homa hone wotu witaęž‰laęž‰ hali make ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰taęž‰ kone anaęž‰e alaęž‰ hali make tikitikinaęž‰ halaęž‰ hali make yakopiki hali make ipikaęž‰ loke handeteke halaęž‰ hali make hapeke yelieke.  
\v 9 Kuta make ipikitaęž‰ mo hande ti lao hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ otaęž‰ pi walaęž‰laęž‰eki daĚ±oĚ±la miniki hapeke yelieke. Kutu pilie ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ tupaęž‰ walolo hataęž‰ tambaęž‰ meaęž‰peke yelieke. Kutupa make mo hande otaęž‰ tupaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ pimanu pa tupaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ kiaaseme wandaęž‰hali tikitiki yaasaęž‰ hali hapeke yelieke.   
\s1 Makeaasaęž‰ haliweki haemekeeki  
\p
\v 10 Haliweki wopumaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi kiaaso hataęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ pa hameke pi manumaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰hali makeao halememe. Kutupiki pi lo haleme mandane haliwekitaęž‰ mo pa sekemesaisi pu haleme Diu tapake haemeke tapakemaęž‰ kone lo halememe.  
\v 11 Kutupiki yalaęž‰ meaęž‰peke haumanu piteleme hautaęž‰ pa yanaaso hataęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ manimanu muluekemaęž‰ pitelememe. Mo walaęž‰peke na yeke pimanu walemeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mandane haliwekinaęž‰ hone make ikaęž‰ wekiwandaęž‰naęž‰ hone make u hoeyaenaęž‰ lo halememe. Kutu paamaęž‰naęž‰ ikaęž‰ lo haleme pimanu saęž‰saęž‰ peaęž‰peke.  
\v 12 Ikaęž‰ Kotiti tapake hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ hone wopu wiki some hataęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ Kotiti tapake paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pimanu dupa leekeme. Kotiti haliweki ikitaęž‰ hoto paeyao ya pi ombu lo halememe. Kutupa ikitaęž‰ hoke sayalemaęž‰ handaęž‰ hataęž‰ weleke pamba pitaęž‰ ne tieke naa sokaęž‰laęž‰ pambeke some hombo hao halememe leekeme.  
\v 13 Koto pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi yeke handaataęž‰ mo Ketiso wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hone tulalemeeki takaęž‰laenaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ pimaęž‰ hando lolenaęž‰e.  
\v 14 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pa pimanu make o otaęž‰ pi na opiki haliwekinaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu make ipua teliaamaęž‰naęž‰ kutu puelenaęž‰e.   
\p
\v 15 Yako piki hau pu halaęž‰ somemaęž‰ paeyaotaęž‰ pa yako pikieki homeke hone u halaęž‰pate pa mo pi na miki haĚ±iĚ±piki hone u halaęž‰ somemaęž‰ paeyaotaęž‰ yako pikieki diaęž‰me hone u halaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke ipikaęž‰ hone witaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make ipikaęž‰ puki make haĚ±iĚ± pitolo pitaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 16 Ikaęž‰ pimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ handolomaęž‰me laa lo halemepate pa ikaęž‰ piteleme hau manumaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ na handelemeeki peneme yao halaęž‰me. Kotaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ honditi honditi wopu pu make pi na opu epeke haumanu peaęž‰paęž‰peketaęž‰ iki anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\c 2  
\s1 Keileke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ manaęž‰ pimanu  
\p
\v 1 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ mo manaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ tupaęž‰ tolu walo hapeke.  
\v 2 Keileke haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ Mo hoke ikali naa keaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me laataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ epeke hau paęž‰taęž‰ tikitiki piki hone witolo make mo ikaęž‰ hone wopu handeteke hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulalemeeki make pukimaęž‰ homelemeeki make kutupa mo ikaęž‰ puki takaęž‰laasaęž‰ hau pitolo pitolo haleme hau make kotaęž‰ hau paeyaonaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ na taĚ±lenaęž‰ leke epeke tupaęž‰ hapaęž‰peke laa walaęž‰peke.   
\p
\v 3 Mo keileke wandaęž‰weki paęž‰taęž‰ make koto tupaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰ Iki make yako piki wandaęž‰weki hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ hapaęž‰peke la alotaęž‰ mo hande keileke wandaęž‰weki paęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ laasaęž‰ hau na pu make mo waini ikalimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone hoeyaamaęž‰naęž‰ wopu na neke hataęž‰ make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo panake wandaęž‰weki paęž‰taęž‰ epeke hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu walaęž‰ tiaapaęž‰peke la walaęž‰peke.  
\v 4 Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo panake wandaęž‰weki paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ haliki wekiwandiki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ make  
\v 5 ikaęž‰ hone handeteke hataęž‰ make ikaęž‰ halemeeki alaęž‰taęž‰ na taĚ±lenaęž‰ leke hataęž‰ make epeke da handeteke halaęž‰ wandaęž‰weki hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ haliki tonu oto paęž‰taęž‰ hao hapaęž‰peke laa walenaęž‰ walo hapeke. Koto panake wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ kutupiki haumanu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo pa wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pimanu paęž‰taęž‰ hoke pi lapeke waleke na wilieke.   
\p
\v 6 Kotaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone mo panake haliweki ikaęž‰ honemanu wopu handeteke haenaęž‰maęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone u tiaapeke.  
\v 7 Nakaęž‰ kone nakaęž‰ pilipi hau paeyaotaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ handaa hondaęž‰mea pu haenaęž‰ epeke hau seliapomanu pu hapeke. Nakaęž‰ pi walaęž‰laęž‰ haunaęž‰ hone wopu wia mo hapeke pitiki pimanu homeke walo hapeke.  
\v 8 Nakaęž‰ lolo pele pi manutaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ la la pu hoeyaamaęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ na taĚ±leke pi manumaęž‰ walo hapeke. Mo nakaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ koto hau handaataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ pitolomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hokeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na handemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me hone witolo yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homilimikie.   
\s1 E pokaasaęž‰ halinaęž‰ manaęž‰ pi  
\p
\v 9 Mo pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ haliweki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ dupiki pi lapeke. Ikaęž‰ e pokemeeki paeyaomaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ haliwekinaęž‰ pi oto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ epeke e pokeme ekimaęž‰ iki taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaapaęž‰peke. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo iki handeteke halaęž‰ haliwekinaęž‰ pi eto eto na lao make  
\v 10 mo ikaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ make pake na napaęž‰peke. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ ki na hake epeke e pokaęž‰laęž‰ hali halaęž‰me hone winaęž‰ ikaęž‰ e pokeleme ekimaęž‰ lenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke. Dupiki haumanu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ koto ikaęž‰ hau paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ Daęž‰taasaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ manaęž‰ pimanu yeiyaęž‰ la walieke.   
\s1 Ketisonaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ nate  
\p
\v 11 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homo tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ kenke wandaęž‰hali paeyao mea daęž‰taaluekemaęž‰ peneme yaęž‰laęž‰eki handolomaęž‰me.  
\v 12 Koto aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homo tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ walotaęž‰ pa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ hoki nane yao nikaęž‰ hoke hone paęž‰laęž‰ haumanu pitolomaęž‰eki make do kenkenaęž‰ hoke hone paęž‰laęž‰ haumanu pitolomaęž‰eki make kiaamono paęž‰laęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ame do kenkenaęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone handeteke hataęž‰ make tondepe pea hataęž‰ make Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hau hone witolo hataęž‰ make kutu pitolo hataęž‰  
\v 13 mo hande otaęž‰ ipilie nate opolo epenaęž‰e laa hone tulaasaęž‰ hataęž‰ yu wia halomaęž‰me. Koto epolo paęž‰laęž‰ natetaęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ tieke make daęž‰taalaęž‰ hali Yesu Ketiso make ipilikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± tieke peneme yaasaęž‰eki opolo ipilieke.  
\v 14 Ketiso ipikitaęž‰ nikinaęž‰ homeekeme. Kutu pieke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ nikitaęž‰ mo hoke hau paęž‰taęž‰ haomeke yokaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ epeke haunaęž‰ puawee hone paęž‰laęž‰ yako piki wandaęž‰hali homeke hamono yeke piekeme.   
\p
\v 15 Do manaęž‰ pimanu walo hapeke. Kutu puluekemaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ pi opitaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hone u tia tia puluekemaęž‰ make hoke haumanu peaamaęž‰naęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ pulu pikaęž‰naęž‰ make nakaęž‰ biki ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ hataęž‰ peaęž‰peke.   
\c 3  
\s1 Ketiso wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke haumanu  
\p
\v 1 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hone u tiatiki pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ kapomani haliweki oto nane make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ telipaalaęž‰ e handeteke haleme haliweki oto nane make hao hapaęž‰peke lapeke. Mo haliwekinaęž‰ kakemaęž‰ homo hataęž‰ hau paeyao epeke tupaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ tikitiki yao hapaęž‰peke lapeke.  
\v 2 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hoke pimanu na leketaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pelia taęž‰maęž‰ni pea hataęž‰ hoto paeyaotaęž‰ paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ yopu aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ hapaęž‰peke lapeke.   
\p
\v 3 Ambaęž‰ niki make hone wopu na wiki pi tunkulu make pu ataęž‰kaęž‰ peaomaęž‰me. Nikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ hau manumaęž‰ make nikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaasaęž‰ haumanu make koto hau paeyaomaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone handeteke haenaęž‰ lomaęž‰me. Kutupa nate paeyao mineke pankaęž‰ tiake pimanu lo make maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ epeke ale paęž‰taęž‰ make leke polopao haomaęž‰me. Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ niki honditi pimikitaęž‰ iki make honditi pu haomaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 4 Kutu pumaęž‰pate mo hande nikaęž‰ daęž‰taasaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki make pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki make peneme yaalo epeke pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰  
\v 5 ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰la tambaęž‰ miekeme. Pa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ epeke hau pumeke handa na pieke yekepate pa mo ipikaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homeeke ekinaęž‰ niki tambaęž‰ miekeme. Kutu piekeeki manutaęž‰ niki panake weki tupaęž‰ daęž‰ta hamono Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Holi Sipitidi paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ tanda paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 6 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ Daęž‰taasaęž‰ Hali Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Holi Sipitidi niki paęž‰taęž‰ anekemaęž‰ wopu tapaeyekeme.  
\v 7 Kutu pieke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Ketiso ipikaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homeeke ekinaęž‰ niki Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ tikitiki pea make nikaęž‰ hone puaasomaęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki make miomono piekeme. Do alaęž‰ pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pie.   
\p
\v 8 Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaaseme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ epeke piteme hau manumaęž‰ mo mandane wandaęž‰hali tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone witolo hataęž‰ waleke halaęž‰tiki pinaęž‰maęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ do wapenaęž‰ alo pimanu iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ wopu laęž‰ moneao hapeke.   
\p
\v 9 Kutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰pate mo epe na piki ape apemanu make mo atekenaęž‰ ateke hatiki epeeke ekinaęž‰ biki eleke eleke mokaęž‰lao haleme ekimanu make mo pi yokaalu alu pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make mo hande Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ lo pimanu wiekeeki dupa ulaęž‰me laa ape ape lo halemeeki make kotaęž‰ hau paeyao pakaęž‰lao pu hapeke. Kotaęž‰ hau manumaęž‰taęž‰ niki epeaapeke anaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 10 Mo Ketiso tapake tekili paaluekemaęž‰ taapaęž‰laęž‰ somemaęž‰ hoto homeke o yaapo tekili peaapeke leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hoto yaapo saęž‰saęž‰ pilipipate pi na opiki pa tepo peao paa piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ nikaęž‰ tapake some diaęž‰me laa hoki walaęž‰peke.  
\v 11 Nakaęž‰ handeleme. Kutu piki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ sometaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoke hau manumaęž‰ kone mea hoeyao keaasaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 12 IĚ±maęž‰ Atemasi o Tikikasi yaapo homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰ tapaowaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ neketaęž‰ mo IĚ± yopua haluaęž‰ Nikopolisi da nane potaęž‰manu weiya aęž‰paęž‰peke. IĚ±maęž‰ mo hande koa ki dinaęž‰taęž‰ koto Nikopolisi da paęž‰taęž‰ halueke loaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hone wilime.  
\v 13 Mo Kapomaninaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki tikitiki yao halaęž‰ hali Senasi make mo hande Apolosi kotaęž‰ hali yaapo ipilikaęž‰ pi walo polo pelepeeki kini pinaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ epeke tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ taapaęž‰peke. Ipilikaęž‰ mea polo pelepe ale manutaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ mea wilipipe laa handaęž‰ handaęž‰peke.   
\p
\v 14 Nikaęž‰ Ketiso tapakemaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ haumanu puluekemaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ nate leke epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke hataęž‰ pinaęž‰ mokaęž‰laęž‰ tiatiki peaęž‰paęž‰peke alee. Kutupa make mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki handaęž‰ peteluekemaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo napeke na pitiki epe na piki haumanu leke na peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 15 Do IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± mandake halomaęž‰ tapakemaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taloe pi laęž‰neaasememe. Kutupa mo neke ameĚ±leĚ± haleme Ketiso yankeketonu paęž‰taęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taloe pi alomaęž‰me laa la halaęž‰peke. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homo tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki taapunaęž‰ hao haenaęž‰e.   